{"tid":415702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"畢業過後，總有理財顧問致電過嚟","createTime":"2017-09-27T08:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T08:04:31.000Z","uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f2eee8dd9b962577f057f27c56ac861c5f856edd","tid":415702,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"早排收到個中學同學message，話唔記得我電話乜乜乜。俾咗我電話佢之後，佢就打嚟寒暄一兩句。原本以為佢打嚟諗住聚舊，點知之後就嚟料「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實我而家做緊獨立理財顧問，即係IFA。唔係話sell你，但&hellip;&hellip;</span></span>。」<br />\n中學啊sir話出嚟做嘢之後，同學搵你多數係賣保險倫敦金，估唔到咁快發生係我身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話用成績睇死人，但佢中學成績嘛嘛。試問有邊個會放心將啲錢交俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起佢同我分析啲理財計劃嗰場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中學講嘢又唔見你咁叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小組討論你又縮埋一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你睇到嘅話都係一句，轉行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔啱食呢行飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腳踏實地撈其他行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}